INSERT INTO debian_repository_release (
            repository_id,
            distribution,
            description,
            origin,
            label,
            version,
            suite,
            codename,
            contents,
            created_at,
            updated_at
        )
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $7, $8, '', NOW(), NOW())
        RETURNING id, distribution
